<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="slight-adj">slight <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /slaɪt/    美 /slaɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>轻微的；少量的：</strong></h4>
<p>very small in degree
反 big </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a slight difference / injury
微小的区别/轻伤</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>without the slightest hesitation
毫不犹豫地</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Although I can walk about, there is still a <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (轻微的) pain in my leg.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. slight  </p></div>